## CRITICAL PROBLEM DISCOVERED
Multiple session sub-pages have `isLabModeEnabled()` checks and will show 'Lab Mode Locked' when accessed with demo session IDs:

| Page | Lab Mode Check Line |
|------|---------------------|
| /sessions/[threadId]/evidence/page.tsx | Line 414 |
| /sessions/[threadId]/test-queue/page.tsx | (likely similar) |
| /sessions/[threadId]/hypothesis/page.tsx | (likely similar) |
