| /sessions/[threadId]/brief/page.tsx | (likely similar) |
| /sessions/[threadId]/agents/page.tsx | (likely similar) |
| /sessions/new/page.tsx | Line 242 |

When a user clicks 'Evidence Pack' on a demo session detail page, they navigate to `/sessions/demo-xxx/evidence` and see... 'Lab Mode Locked'. This is jarring and breaks the demo experience.

## Solution: Graceful Degradation Pattern
Instead of full demo mode support (which would require fixtures for each sub-feature), implement a consistent 'Demo Preview' pattern:

